<sect1 id="dir_991442008f2dac028067584555d54581_1autotoc_md143">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::combat::components</title><para>Combat-specific components for aiming, shooting, and attack tracking.</para>
<para>These components implement high-level combat behaviors that coordinate between input, physics, and rendering systems.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_991442008f2dac028067584555d54581_1autotoc_md144">
<title>Components</title><para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Component  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Description  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>Aim2DComponent</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Stores 2D aim direction and fire frequency  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ShootComponent</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Manages projectile shooting with cooldown timer  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>LastAttackerComponent</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Tracks the last entity that attacked this entity  </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_991442008f2dac028067584555d54581_1autotoc_md145">
<title>LastAttackerComponent</title><para>Stores an <computeroutput>AttackContext</computeroutput> containing:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Source entity handle (the attacker)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Contact point (where the attack landed)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Damage applied</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Used by <computeroutput>HealthUpdateSystem</computeroutput> to include attack context in <computeroutput>DeathEvent</computeroutput> for kill attribution and scoring.</para>
<para><hruler/>
